name: Grilled Chicken and Vegetable Kebabs

ingredients.name: Fajita Seasoning or Shish Kebab Seasoning
assorted vegetables (mushrooms, onion, bell peppers, zucchini)

preparation:
1. Add oil, white balsamic vinegar and half of Fajita Seasoning to a sealable, food-safe plastic bag or large mixing bowl.
  2. Add chicken, toss to coat and marinate in refrigerator. Meanwhile, soak bamboo skewers in water.
  3. Preheat grill to medium-high. Remove chicken and discard marinade.
  4. Alternately thread 2–3 vegetable pieces and 1 chicken piece on Bamboo Skewers. Lightly sprinkle with remaining Fajita Seasoning.
  5. Grill kebabs, turning frequently, for 10-15 minutes, or until chicken is cooked through.
tips: For moist, juicy, full-flavoured chicken, let marinate for a minimum of 30 minutes.
